claim: Flublok contains 45 micrograms (mcg) of HA per strain vs 15 mcg of HA per strain in a standard-dose influenza vaccine.
explanation: Page 2 of an MMWR clinical recommendations document showing the table of contents, introductory text on CDC adoption of ACIP recommendations, publication attribution, suggested citation, and editorial staff listings.
